Title: The Gravity of Love
---
You are the one
who falls so that

You can find me in
the deep and down-

ward tumble of life,
like a stone that

descends in tend-
ing ever down

to where it comes
to rest, and just so,

there where I fall
is where You

wait and how
You call.
